      "content": "i get that it was messy, but wasnt the main goal to prevent a massive humanitarian disaster and stop a massacre in benghazi? if they had just sat back and let gaddafi do what he said he was gonna do, wouldnt that have been a much bigger strategic and moral failure for the west?",
